## PHASE 5 — AGENT LAYER (LAST)
Now a clean typed module tree exists with real gates. Build _config/ description docs + .claude/workflows/ orchestrators. Split every planned guard: mechanical -> script exit-code check (not an agent); judgment -> scoped LLM agent. Filesystem handoffs, not chat handoffs. Prove ONE generator->guard->exit-code loop end-to-end before cloning. Halt-and-surface to me after N failures; never loop indefinitely.
GATE: one loop verified on a trivial real ticket (file appears on disk; downstream step hard-fails if it's missing; forced failure trips the exit code; max-pass halts) before any second loop is built.

